<item><title>Post</title><link>https://tlhg.org/post/58449611459/went-in-to-wake-gus-up-from-a-3-hour-nap-after/</link><guid>https://tlhg.org/post/58449611459/went-in-to-wake-gus-up-from-a-3-hour-nap-after/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2013 21:24:00 +0000</pubDate><description>&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Went in to wake Gus up from a 3-hour nap after spending the first half of the day at Magic Kingdom.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Me: You ready to go back and ride some more rides?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Gus (half-whining): I&amp;rsquo;m dooone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Me: You&amp;rsquo;re done what?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Gus: Diiisney.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;(Five minutes later he bounded out of the room, ready for more.)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item>
